{"tid":1533031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人依然覺得太子站有黑警打死左人","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:32:45.000Z","uid":10905,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"32befc7298e06ca641011e2ca19d4003ac645fcd","tid":1533031,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"第一你解釋唔到點解要封站封足一日<br />\n第二你解釋唔到點解連救護都唔比入<br />\n第三訓左係度果個義士仍然唔知係邊個而加係邊<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔需要fc亦冇得fc<br />\n但我覺得HA應該冇講大話<br />\n因為分分鐘連佢都唔知<br />\n<br />\n要fc令人信服麻煩黑警自己搵黨鐵拎cctv公開出黎<br />\n並立即帶果位被捕者上庭<br />\n<br />\n否則我相信好多人都會覺得黑警(定係其他人士？)<br />\n係有打死人"},{"pid":"5ea5422e9eeef17fa895557a9794769eaf74017e","tid":1533031,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"有咩要做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532957</a>"},{"pid":"389d24184f9458151aba28d921f7b8e3e53be21d","tid":1533031,"uid":132497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"d5682f007a52f17d6650b13d87fdb489011b8d4d","tid":1533031,"ui